HBO & Co to buy Management Software . HBO & Co said on Friday it had signed a letter of intent to acquire Management Software Inc ( MSI ) , a privately held provider of software solutions for the homecare industry . The company said in a statement MSI shareholders would get about 890 , 000 shares of HBO stock in the transaction . HBO shares ended down 2 - 5 / 8 at $ 50 - 1 / 2 on Thursday on the Nasdaq Stock Market . The acquisition is subject to completion of a definitive agreement and regulatory approval . It is scheduled to be completed during the third quarter . Management Software , based in Springfield , Mo . , had 1995 revenue of $ 15 million and has over 200 employees . - - New York newsroom , ( 212 ) 859 - 1610 
